  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decipher the puzzles of an ancient maze to save your soul.</h2><br>You and your partner awake on separate sides of a mysterious maze. Surrounded by shadows, spectral whispers, and magical orbs that help you communicate with each other, the two of you must traverse the winding corridors and find a way out. The only question that remains… will your soul be saved?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/f3329c1eb47fea3df3b9ce5fa93dc86b.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/f3329c1eb47fea3df3b9ce5fa93dc86b.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/f3329c1eb47fea3df3b9ce5fa93dc86b.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tvö is a cooperative puzzle game. Two players find themselves trapped on opposite sides of an elaborate maze. Together, they must solve puzzles hidden in its depths in order to discover a way out. Both sides of the maze have their own secrets that the players can find.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Communicate</h2><i>Only your words and wits can save you now.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/73681f74351ff5424e5d92dfe17530aa.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/73681f74351ff5424e5d92dfe17530aa.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/73681f74351ff5424e5d92dfe17530aa.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Through floating orbs, the mysterious maze lets you talk to your partner on the other side. Use your communication skills to solve the puzzles you will face.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve</h2><i>The way to salvation is teeming with trials.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/5496ec1d049939ba8dbeb2fea5f65995.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/5496ec1d049939ba8dbeb2fea5f65995.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/5496ec1d049939ba8dbeb2fea5f65995.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Work together with your partner to unravel the puzzles laid throughout the maze. What your partner experiences will be crucial to your success.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere</h2><i>You and your partner are not alone…</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/8059020b4ab0d01933fbfb7d489e14fb.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/8059020b4ab0d01933fbfb7d489e14fb.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/8059020b4ab0d01933fbfb7d489e14fb.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the corridors of the maze to find those that came before, and those that still remain. Immerse yourself in the dark ambience of the maze.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decipher the puzzles of an ancient maze to save your soul.</h2><br>You and your partner awake on separate sides of a mysterious maze. Surrounded by shadows, spectral whispers, and magical orbs that help you communicate with each other, the two of you must traverse the winding corridors and find a way out. The only question that remains… will your soul be saved?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/f3329c1eb47fea3df3b9ce5fa93dc86b.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/f3329c1eb47fea3df3b9ce5fa93dc86b.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/f3329c1eb47fea3df3b9ce5fa93dc86b.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tvö is a cooperative puzzle game. Two players find themselves trapped on opposite sides of an elaborate maze. Together, they must solve puzzles hidden in its depths in order to discover a way out. Both sides of the maze have their own secrets that the players can find.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Communicate</h2><i>Only your words and wits can save you now.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/73681f74351ff5424e5d92dfe17530aa.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/73681f74351ff5424e5d92dfe17530aa.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/73681f74351ff5424e5d92dfe17530aa.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Through floating orbs, the mysterious maze lets you talk to your partner on the other side. Use your communication skills to solve the puzzles you will face.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve</h2><i>The way to salvation is teeming with trials.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/5496ec1d049939ba8dbeb2fea5f65995.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/5496ec1d049939ba8dbeb2fea5f65995.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/5496ec1d049939ba8dbeb2fea5f65995.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Work together with your partner to unravel the puzzles laid throughout the maze. What your partner experiences will be crucial to your success.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere</h2><i>You and your partner are not alone…</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/8059020b4ab0d01933fbfb7d489e14fb.poster.avif?t=1697513797\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/8059020b4ab0d01933fbfb7d489e14fb.webm?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2026990/extras/8059020b4ab0d01933fbfb7d489e14fb.mp4?t=1697513797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the corridors of the maze to find those that came before, and those that still remain. Immerse yourself in the dark ambience of the maze.",
